
Simple collection of scripts and utilities useful to the author.


Contents
--------

make-pod
  Make POD documentation from our library files.

sync-examples
  Use rsync to promote our examples to the slaughter website.

test-packaging
  Test that the packaging primitives can be used to detect package
  installation.  Added after the API was reworked to ease my concerns.

test-git-transport
test-hg-transport
test-http-transport
test-local-transport
test-rsync-transport
  Test the transport referenced in the name of the script by creating
  and using a trash repository built on the fly.

  NOTE: These will create/delete files/directories so read source before invoking.



